text: The Institut supérieur de management was the business school of the Versailles Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines University.UNIVERSITÉ DE VERSAILLES SAINT-QUENTIN- EN-YVELINES - UVSQ Created in 2010, the school was located in Guyancourt. In 2019, it joined the IAE's network and became the IAE Versailles. == References == Category:Versailles Saint-Quentin-en-Yvelines University Category:Education in Yvelines Category:Educational institutions established in 2010
title: Institut supérieur de management
